examples.en: Bear right when the road divides.
A tall fence divides the two yards.
The river divides after the bridge.
Three divides into nine three times.
Here, the river divides into three channels.
The mountain range divides the two countries.
She divides her time between New York and Paris.
The equator divides the Earth into two hemispheres.
This dilatation divides the digestive canal into three parts.
The river divides here, but the two streams rejoin downstream.
